  m_Name: Sabotage!
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Seed
  title: Sabotage!
  description: High Pontiff, dire tidings have reached our ears. A rival sect has
    infiltrated a workshop owned by one of the faithful. By tampering with the heavy
    tools, they have caused a most grievous accident, claiming the life of a craftsman.
    The remaining laborers refuse to return to their stations until their safety
    is guaranteed. Should we fail to intervene, the foundry may close its doors forever.
